        <section class='think'>
            <div id='spiegazione'>
                <p>
                    What is your goal? What do you want to achieve and when? How much will it cost
                    and what other support you may need (perhaps, some materials, teachers etc.)? Keep
                    it simple, keep it phased. Plan for a year and say what you achieve in each quarter.
                    A project of 500 EUR will be easier to fund than a project of 2000 EUR. Think through
                    what you need most.
                </p>
                <p class='i'>
                    EXAMPLE: If you want to take 40 children on a one day coach trip, explain why they should
                    go - what they get from the trip, how you will choose the 40, when the trip is expected
                    to take place and the calculated price of the trip (coach with the driver or
                    anything else?)
                </p>
